1233→
1234→/* ==========================================================================
1235→   UTILITIES LAYER
1236→   Helper classes. These have the highest layer priority.
1237→   ========================================================================== */
1238→
1239→@layer utilities {
1240→  /* Visually hidden -- accessible to screen readers but not visible.
